Title:  The wreckers against the builders

Tags:   value creation

Featured: false

Recommended: false

Author: Kurt Vonnegut

Date:   2008

Work Title: The Unicorn Trap

Date Added: 2026-04-21 11:55:42 -0700

Body:

"The wreckers against the builders!" said Elmer. "There's the whole story of life!"

"I am not going to help the wreckers," said Elmer. "My son and I are builders."
